# Ghost Research Core - Unified API Tests

@base_url = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Root / Health Check
GET {{base_url}}/
Accept: application/json

### Health Check (Alternative)
GET {{base_url}}/health
Accept: application/json

### ===========================================================================
### CYBERRADAR INTELLIGENCE (RESEARCH)
### ===========================================================================

### Get API Info
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/info
Accept: application/json

### Get Critical Threats
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/threats/critical?days=7
Accept: application/json

### Threat Statistics
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/threats/statistics
Accept: application/json

### Chat with Cyber Assistant (French)
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/research/chatbot/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Qu'est-ce qu'un ransomware ?",
  "language": "fr",
  "educational_mode": true
}

### Get Educational Glossary
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/educational/glossary?query=phishing
Accept: application/json

### Get Latest Trend Analysis
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/trends/latest
Accept: application/json

### ===========================================================================
### SECURE RAG ASSISTANT
### ===========================================================================

### Secure Query (RAG + Security Filters)
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/rag/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Quelles sont les meilleures pratiques pour sécuriser une base de données ?",
  "user_id": "test-user-001"
}

### Security Status
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/rag/security/status
Accept: application/json

### Generate Security Report
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/rag/security/report
Accept: application/json

### ===========================================================================
### INFRASTRUCTURE & MONITORING
### ===========================================================================

### Prometheus Metrics
GET {{base_url}}/metrics
Accept: application/json
